{"tid":681800,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女生們，請你們要學識處理孤獨","createTime":"2018-05-28T10:38:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T16:35:09.000Z","uid":188428,"like":100,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f548b4690231deaefd8c48ef8ce40fe9e6846497","tid":681800,"uid":188428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T10:38:31.000Z","msg":"當關係走到唔再係熱戀期嗰種日痴夜痴嘅階段<br />\n大家除咗拍拖 各自都會有朋友圈子要維繫<br />\n選擇找伴侶或朋友<br />\n係一個互耗性嘅競爭<br />\n陪A就陪唔到B 反之亦然<br />\n<br />\n一個人嘅健康交際<br />\n係需要擁有伴侶同埋朋友<br />\n兩者缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n男人想被尊重 女人想被愛<br />\n當男人同其他frd social緊嘅時候<br />\n佢就淨係想用嗰段時間 專注同frd玩<br />\n佢可以將其他日子嘅時間拎嚟陪你<br />\n但今晚佢淨係想專心同frd吹水<br />\n<br />\n如果你係一個愛你男朋友嘅女仔<br />\n請你喺呢一段時間 <br />\n自己搵其他嘢做<br />\n上網睇片 聽歌 做吓運動 諸如此類<br />\n請你做其他嘢分散注意力<br />\n唔好奪命追魂call<br />\n唔好鑽牛角尖覺得佢今晚唔理你<br />\n然後越諗越衰 覺得佢唔愛你<br />\n<br />\n我知道你好掛住男朋友<br />\n有嘢好想同佢傾訴<br />\n好想喺佢身上索取安全感<br />\n好想佢關注你<br />\n<br />\n但係<br />\n請你要學識處理孤獨<br />\n因為對男人嚟講<br />\n你喺度哭哭鬧鬧<br />\n或者因為一晚而耿耿於懷嘅話<br />\n男人可能會出於愛你而氹返你<br />\n但心底裏<br />\n男人會分辨到<br />\n你係一個唔成熟嘅妹妹仔<br />\n<br />\n你可能會覺得<br />\n「當我需要佢嘅時候，佢冇出現」<br />\n然後因此悶悶不樂<br />\n甚至私底下去搵其他異性傾訴<br />\n因為「你需要陪伴嘅時候，佢哋喺度」<br />\n但呢個只係一個幼稚嘅藉口<br />\n<br />\n兩個人相處<br />\n冇可能有一個人永遠陪住你<br />\n人作為獨立個體<br />\n係會有佢自己嘅生活<br />\n<br />\n調轉角色諗吓<br />\n你都會同班姊妹去shopping去玩啦<br />\n設想吓如果男友不停追call<br />\n又因為你唔喺度而即刻頹晒<br />\n甚至秋後算帳的話<br />\n你豈會不覺大煞風景？<br />\n覺得男友「不成熟」？<br />\n<br />\n對男人嚟講，個感覺一模一樣。<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n你應接受 他不能永遠陪著你<br />\n你應理解 即使他不能時時刻刻陪伴你 也不代表他不愛你<br />\n<br />\n請你學懂處理孤獨<br />\n這是令關係走得長遠的特質<br />\n若你因為短暫索取不到安全感<br />\n而吵吵鬧鬧 或耿耿於懷<br />\n只會顯得你是一個不成熟的妹妹仔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n女友耿耿於懷緊，又要氹<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78fed1ece305a4f3723e4c182f3c4c84a85d0897","tid":681800,"uid":170616,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T10:48:27.000Z","msg":"調轉角色諗吓<br />\n你都會同班姊妹去shopping去玩啦<br />\n設想吓如果男友不停追call<br />\n又因為你唔喺度而即刻頹晒<br />\n<br />\n如果唔會唔開心甚至好開心咁係咪可以合理化女生唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53dc09f361d904a3596e64d5a9dbf22d876130e4","tid":681800,"uid":188428,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"78fed1ece305a4f3723e4c182f3c4c84a85d0897","tid":681800,"uid":170616,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T10:48:27.000Z","msg":"調轉角色諗吓<br />\n你都會同班姊妹去shopping去玩啦<br />\n設想吓如果男友不停追call<br />\n又因為你唔喺度而即刻頹晒<br />\n<br />\n如果唔會唔開心甚至好開心咁係咪可以合理化女生唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T10:51:09.000Z","msg":"講得啱<br />\n呢個例子忽略了男女心理結構天生不同<br />\n舉的不好<br />\n<br />\n女仔鍾意男仔擔心自己<br />\n但男仔會想有獨立嘅時間 獨立嘅圈子<br />\n如果女仔係愛個男朋友<br />\n就請明白呢個道理"},{"pid":"67f047261548a186203aef56d4310d5250c7256b","tid":681800,"uid":77473,"like":33,"dislike":4,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T10:54:31.000Z","msg":"唔鐘意咪分手囉 <br />\n我處理到孤獨就唔洗拍拖啦<br />\n貪你條J 又短又軟呀？"},{"pid":"a7da7d803dcd3121e0ce0e702ddb8e8621f73d2c","tid":681800,"uid":13474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T11:00:14.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"44787435b002aff7eccdc10a4f3ed06f02fa2424","tid":681800,"uid":170616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T11:12:07.000Z","msg":"咁如果女生過程中完全無打比佢 無sd message騷擾佢 淨係要求佢飲完野番到屋企講聲 而男生直接失蹤成晚第二朝先覆 又可唔可以應用係你依到 女生唔應該介意 依個都係一個要自己處理既孤獨感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"275236115c87e1a8c4b96df0361728f7898db6ab","tid":681800,"uid":188428,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"67f047261548a186203aef56d4310d5250c7256b","tid":681800,"uid":77473,"like":33,"dislike":4,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T10:54:31.000Z","msg":"唔鐘意咪分手囉 <br />\n我處理到孤獨就唔洗拍拖啦<br />\n貪你條J 又短又軟呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T11:29:59.000Z","msg":"我就係想整治你呢種mindset<br />\n<br />\n啱啱認識佢嘅你<br />\n大多係因為見識到佢嘅魅力而鍾情於佢<br />\n依家你要佢時時刻刻陪你<br />\n連佢最後少少嘅空間都被搾壓埋<br />\n其實係扭曲緊佢嘅本性<br />\n<br />\n人相處耐咗，總會遇上短暫分開嘅時刻<br />\n我唔係叫你處理永世嘅孤獨<br />\n而係適當處理短短一晚 佢出去朋友聚會嘅時間<br />\n或者長至幾個月 佢去公幹嘅日子<br />\n以積極態度正面處理<br />\n讓呢份感情可以繼續走落去<br />\n<br />\n你真心寧願男朋友放棄自己嘅生活圈子<br />\n放棄自己嘅興趣嚟陪你?<br />\n<br />\n如果有一個男人<br />\n係可以時時刻刻陪你嘅話<br />\n隨傳隨到 永遠on call<br />\n冇自己興趣 冇自己要做嘅事<br />\n一世淨係做你嘅傀儡同公仔<br />\n咁佢應該係一個冇用嘅廢物<br />\n要你同一個廢男人相處 <br />\n你又甘心咩?"},{"pid":"166c9817109859b2dfbfbfb83d035539c45adab9","tid":681800,"uid":188428,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"44787435b002aff7eccdc10a4f3ed06f02fa2424","tid":681800,"uid":170616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T11:12:07.000Z","msg":"咁如果女生過程中完全無打比佢 無sd message騷擾佢 淨係要求佢飲完野番到屋企講聲 而男生直接失蹤成晚第二朝先覆 又可唔可以應用係你依到 女生唔應該介意 依個都係一個要自己處理既孤獨感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T11:44:40.000Z","msg":"不論男女<br />\n冇合理就失蹤成晚<br />\n係不重視，不尊重伴侶嘅表現<br />\n介意當然合理"},{"pid":"6394cc42f45363d69b7a88792e2b55a38cedb5db","tid":681800,"uid":37940,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T12:11:58.000Z","msg":"都唔係淨係女仔，所有人都要學識點處理孤獨啦"},{"pid":"e02316cbe027b396788ee63983334dd5beb720fa","tid":681800,"uid":57848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T12:24:04.000Z","msg":"還是會寂寞 - 陳綺貞<br />\n<br />\n也曾想過躲進別人溫暖的懷中<br />\n可是這麼一來就一點意義也沒有<br />\n我的高尚情操一直不斷提醒著我<br />\n離開你的我不論過多久還是會寂寞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n男又好女又好，學識自己排解寂寞，就唔孤獨。<br />\n<br />\n對方唔係你嘅空氣，而滋潤你嘅春雨。"},{"pid":"ff9c89afae4ab76e9074c64fb661ff241400e388","tid":681800,"uid":22560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T12:25:07.000Z","msg":"唔應該用孤獨呢個字 <br />\n應該用獨處<br />\n男朋友唔喺身邊唔等於一定會孤獨喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24959e03845eb715fa9d7fdb5ff850172428740f","tid":681800,"uid":186296,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T12:36:05.000Z","msg":"點解呢個世界的情人唔可以將對話透明化,一定要收收埋埋先過癮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccde6a7fbc685289be29b2e132ab4748dd3a5ddc","tid":681800,"uid":75500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T12:42:01.000Z","msg":"唉屌 完全明白<br />\n而家同fd出去都要偷偷地出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲衰過坐監"},{"pid":"23f629628ec67fa6b22b2887d90dca22af4b21d5","tid":681800,"uid":188428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ccde6a7fbc685289be29b2e132ab4748dd3a5ddc","tid":681800,"uid":75500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T12:42:01.000Z","msg":"唉屌 完全明白<br />\n而家同fd出去都要偷偷地出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲衰過坐監"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T12:48:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n勸你同佢講清楚<br />\n如果佢明智嘅話<br />\n佢會明白理解<br />\n以後體諒多少少你<br />\n<br />\n如果佢港女格<br />\n咁你就自求多福喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以我開po<br />\n希望以外人身份<br />\n教育其他女仔"},{"pid":"e6d6aa5d5ead18f3c57946b50366f4a02c7be49f","tid":681800,"uid":204700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T16:06:22.000Z","msg":"她終究還是學不懂，<br />\n所以走了。"},{"pid":"d77361997a18052b22654d7212fd4f13a2c27bee","tid":681800,"uid":204700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T16:10:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f8fb667ec5d5e477ca1709db8d9ec7e88ea237e","tid":681800,"uid":198065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T06:49:23.000Z","msg":"寫得幾好啊<br />\n<br />\n明就明，做唔做到又係另一件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe273cdc9870e7ad5fed2b9aee6bd341b1ce449a","tid":681800,"uid":204700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1f8fb667ec5d5e477ca170